* play: constant full-screen redraw

* win32/play: full prefetch

* play: snapshots are created but not used

* win32/play: ugly cursor

* win32/rec: on Win95/98/ME, scrolling does a full screen dump

* win32/play: no way to select the plugin except for file extensions

* rec,proxy: no --append

* unix/rec: no information about UTF-8
* unix/rec: SIGINT and friends should be passed to the child

* docs: no manpages

* docs: no README
